<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Comprehensive Health Onboarding - FitWit AI</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: rgb(18, 17, 17);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .particles {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(180deg); opacity: 0.8; }
        }
        .onboarding-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: white;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            animation: slideInDown 1s ease-out;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            animation: slideInUp 1s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }
        @keyframes slideInDown {
            from { transform: translateY(-50px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }
        @keyframes slideInUp {
            from { transform: translateY(50px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }
        .progress-container {
            background: rgba(246, 242, 242, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: slideInLeft 1s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }
        .step-indicator {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .progress-line {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(243, 240, 240, 0.3);
            border-radius: 2px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4CAF50, #8BC34A);
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: width 0.8s ease;
            width: 12.5%;
        }
        .step {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .step.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #8BC34A);
            border-color: #4CAF50;
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.5);
        }
        .step.completed {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #8BC34A);
            border-color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .progress-text {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from { transform: translateX(-50px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
        }
        .form-step {
            background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: slideInRight 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        @keyframes slideInRight {
            from { transform: translateX(50px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
        }
        .form-step.hidden {
            display: none;
        }
        .form-step h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        .form-group input,
        .form-group select,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: white;
        }
        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #4CAF50;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .conditions-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .condition-item {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        .condition-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .condition-item.selected {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #8BC34A);
            color: white;
            border-color: #4CAF50;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }
        .condition-item i {
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        .rating-scale {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 10px;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .rating-item {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        .rating-item:hover {
            background: #e9ecef;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .rating-item.selected {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #8BC34A);
            color: white;
            border-color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .navigation-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 40px;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .btn:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }
        .btn:hover:before {
            left: 100%;
        }
        .btn.btn-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c757d, #5a6268);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn.btn-secondary:disabled {
            background: #e9ecef;
            color: #6c757d;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }
        .btn.btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #8BC34A);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn.btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35, #F7931E);
            color: white;
        }
        .download-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #17a2b8, #138496);
            color: white;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .completion-screen {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .completion-screen i {
            font-size: 5em;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        }
        .health-tip {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd, #bbdefb);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #2196F3;
        }
        .health-tip i {
            color: #2196F3;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .conditions-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .rating-scale {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .step-indicator {
                overflow-x: auto;
                padding-bottom: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="particles" id="particles"></div>
    <div class="onboarding-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> FitWit AI</h1>
            <p>Comprehensive Health Assessment & Personalized Wellness Journey</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-container">
            <div class="step-indicator">
                <div class="progress-line">
                    <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="step active" data-step="1">1</div>
                <div class="step" data-step="2">2</div>
                <div class="step" data-step="3">3</div>
                <div class="step" data-step="4">4</div>
                <div class="step" data-step="5">5</div>
                <div class="step" data-step="6">6</div>
                <div class="step" data-step="7">7</div>
                <div class="step" data-step="8">8</div>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-text">
                Step <span id="currentStep">1</span> of 8 - <span id="stepTitle">Personal Information</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 1: Personal Information -->
        <div class="form-step" data-step="1">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Personal Information</h2>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="firstName">First Name *</label>
                    <input type="text" id="firstName" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="lastName">Last Name *</label>
                    <input type="text" id="lastName" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="age">Age *</label>
                    <input type="number" id="age" min="1" max="120" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="gender">Gender *</label>
                    <select id="gender" required>
                        <option value="">Select gender</option>
                        <option value="male">Male</option>
                        <option value="female">Female</option>
                        <option value="other">Other</option>
                        <option value="prefer-not-to-say">Prefer not to say</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="occupation">Occupation</label>
                <input type="text" id="occupation" placeholder="What do you do for work?">
            </div>
            <div class="health-tip">
                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                <strong>Health Tip:</strong> Providing accurate personal information helps us create a personalized health plan.
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 2: Physical Metrics -->
        <div class="form-step hidden" data-step="2">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-weight"></i> Physical Metrics</h2>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="height">Height (cm) *</label>
                    <input type="number" id="height" min="100" max="250" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="weight">Weight (kg) *</label>
                    <input type="number" id="weight" min="30" max="300" step="0.1" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="targetWeight">Target Weight (kg)</label>
                    <input type="number" id="targetWeight" min="30" max="300" step="0.1">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="bodyType">Body Type</label>
                    <select id="bodyType">
                        <option value="">Select body type</option>
                        <option value="ectomorph">Ectomorph (Naturally thin)</option>
                        <option value="mesomorph">Mesomorph (Athletic build)</option>
                        <option value="endomorph">Endomorph (Naturally broader)</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How would you describe your current fitness level?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="fitnessLevel">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="1">Sedentary<br><small>No exercise</small></div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="2">Lightly Active<br><small>1-3 days/week</small></div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="3">Moderately Active<br><small>3-5 days/week</small></div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="4">Very Active<br><small>6-7 days/week</small></div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="5">Extremely Active<br><small>2x per day</small></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="health-tip">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                <strong>Health Tip:</strong> Your BMI will be calculated automatically to help assess your health status.
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 3: Medical History -->
        <div class="form-step hidden" data-step="3">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i> Medical History</h2>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Do you have any of the following medical conditions? (Select all that apply)</label>
                <div class="conditions-grid" data-field="medicalConditions">
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="diabetes">
                        <i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i>
                        <span>Diabetes</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="hypertension">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                        <span>High Blood Pressure</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="heart-disease">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart-pulse"></i>
                        <span>Heart Disease</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="asthma">
                        <i class="fas fa-lungs"></i>
                        <span>Asthma</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="arthritis">
                        <i class="fas fa-bone"></i>
                        <span>Arthritis</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="osteoporosis">
                        <i class="fas fa-skeleton"></i>
                        <span>Osteoporosis</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="thyroid">
                        <i class="fas fa-pills"></i>
                        <span>Thyroid Issues</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="depression">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                        <span>Depression/Anxiety</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="medications">Current Medications (List all)</label>
                <textarea id="medications" rows="3" placeholder="List any medications you're currently taking..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="allergies">Known Allergies</label>
                <textarea id="allergies" rows="3" placeholder="List any known allergies..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="surgeries">Previous Surgeries</label>
                <textarea id="surgeries" rows="3" placeholder="List any previous surgeries or major medical procedures..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="health-tip">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <strong>Health Tip:</strong> Complete medical history helps ensure your fitness plan is safe and effective.
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 4: Lifestyle & Habits -->
        <div class="form-step hidden" data-step="4">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Lifestyle & Habits</h2>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How many hours do you sleep per night on average?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="sleepHours">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="1">4-5 hours</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="2">5-6 hours</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="3">6-7 hours</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="4">7-8 hours</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="5">8+ hours</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How would you rate your sleep quality?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="sleepQuality">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="1">Very Poor</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="2">Poor</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="3">Fair</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="4">Good</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="5">Excellent</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How many glasses of water do you drink daily?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="waterIntake">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="1">1-2 glasses</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="2">3-4 glasses</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="3">5-6 glasses</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="4">7-8 glasses</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="5">9+ glasses</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Do you smoke?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="smoking">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="never">Never</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="former">Former smoker</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="occasional">Occasionally</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="regular">Regularly</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How often do you consume alcohol?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="alcohol">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="never">Never</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="rarely">Rarely</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="weekly">Weekly</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="daily">Daily</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="health-tip">
                <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                <strong>Health Tip:</strong> Lifestyle factors like sleep, hydration, and substance use impact overall health.
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 5: Diet & Nutrition -->
        <div class="form-step hidden" data-step="5">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-apple-alt"></i> Diet & Nutrition</h2>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>What is your current diet type?</label>
                <div class="conditions-grid" data-field="dietType">
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="omnivore">
                        <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
                        <span>Omnivore</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="vegetarian">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                        <span>Vegetarian</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="vegan">
                        <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
                        <span>Vegan</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="keto">
                        <i class="fas fa-bacon"></i>
                        <span>Ketogenic</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="paleo">
                        <i class="fas fa-drumstick-bite"></i>
                        <span>Paleo</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="mediterranean">
                        <i class="fas fa-fish"></i>
                        <span>Mediterranean</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How many meals do you eat per day?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="mealsPerDay">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="1">1 meal</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="2">2 meals</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="3">3 meals</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="4">4-5 meals</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="5">6+ meals</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How often do you eat fruits and vegetables?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="fruitsVeggies">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="1">Rarely</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="2">1-2 times/week</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="3">3-4 times/week</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="4">Daily</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="5">Multiple times daily</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>How often do you eat fast food or processed meals?</label>
                <div class="rating-scale" data-field="fastFood">
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="1">Daily</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="2">Few times/week</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="3">Weekly</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="4">Monthly</div>
                    <div class="rating-item" data-value="5">Rarely/Never</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="foodAllergies">Food Allergies or Intolerances</label>
                <textarea id="foodAllergies" rows="3" placeholder="List any food allergies or intolerances..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="health-tip">
                <i class="fas fa-carrot"></i>
                <strong>Health Tip:</strong> A balanced diet with plenty of fruits and vegetables is key to energy and health.
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 6: Exercise & Activity -->
        <div class="form-step hidden" data-step="6">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i> Exercise & Physical Activity</h2>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>What types of exercise do you currently do? (Select all that apply)</label>
                <div class="conditions-grid" data-field="exerciseTypes">
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="cardio">
                        <i class="fas fa-running"></i>
                        <span>Cardio/Running</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="weightlifting">
                        <i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i>
                        <span>Weight Lifting</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="condition-item" data-value="yoga">
                        <i class="fas fa-peace"></i>
